data.title: Tony Lewis as Robbie Williams
data.text:
Prepare for an electrifying performance and boundless energy with Tony Lewis and Band as he channels the essence of Robbie Williams for an unforgettable debut performance on the BIBIS stage.

Brace yourself for a lineup featuring iconic hits like “Angels”, “Feel”, “Rock DJ”, and “Let Me Entertain You”. From timeless classics to chart-topping anthems, Tony captivates the stage with the same spirit and charisma that defines Robbie Williams. Join us for an evening of pure entertainment leaving you dancing, singing and craving an encore.
